        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-05-07 12:57:54.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/sdc-master-verify-java/6043/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/sdc-master-verify-java/6043",
